  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "アルカノイドの続編。ブロック崩しゲームの進化版でパワーアップやボス戦が追加。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "アルカノイドの続編。新しいステージとパワーアップが追加。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Eons have passed... yet despite apparent annihilation in the original ARKANOID game, Dimension-controlling force DOH has come back to life, and occupying the huge spacecraft ZARG, has entered our universe. ARKANOID-type spacefighter MIXTEC runs through long forgotten computer data until it finds the answer to this threat... VAUS 2 is launched and speeds towards the threatening alien presence, before it can extract its revenge... \"Arkanoid II\"!\n\nUnlike the original game, the sequel was released only in Japan.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The mysterious enemy known as DOH has returned to seek vengeance on the Vaus space vessel. The player must once again take control of the Vaus (paddle) and overcome many challenges in order to destroy DOH once and for all. Revenge of Doh sees the player battle through 34 rounds, taken from a grand total of 64.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
    {
      "text": "Arkanoid: Revenge of Doh (also known as Arkanoid 2) is an arcade game released by Taito in 1987 as a sequel to Arkanoid.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    }
  ],
  "first_release_date": "1987-05-20",
